{"tid":1725383,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］手足十戎歌","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:04:32.000Z","uid":172102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d01eb73031745070655b81776a83f203f85025d5","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"首先，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝</span></strong></span>各區各大學手足連日來死守勇抗警甴，中大bb硬食2000幾發TG，真係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。係國際上嘅所有示威黎講，中大人呢大仗真係算超水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔怪得外國都學我地起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n無論今日開始出左咩差池都好，由呢刻開始，<br />\n只要你係問心無愧嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真&middot;手足</span></strong></span>，我地都<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔割</span></span>！ <br />\n<br />\n運動經過左就快半年走到呢步，點都會有啲不足出現，但我地每次都好快有改善，有新玩法去克服瓶頸位，關關難過關關過。原因好簡單，因為我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠團結</span></span></strong>。即使想法有落差，但信念一致不變！ 我地無大台，但做到好多意想不到嘅效果，因為我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠自律</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想一眾連登仔女集體構思一個十誡歌/口訣比大家上時戰場用，唔係話要制造太多規限，而係作為一個落場後對自己嘅提醒。因為場上有太多變數，而情緒繃緊嘅情況下，有時自己做啲唔係最好嘅決定自己都唔知。呢隻歌就係希望用黎作為你腦入面最後一道防線，提翻自己有咩真係避免做，有咩必須記得要做。正如行軍打仗，都會有軍訓，當然軍訓好死板，亦太多唔合理嘅地方，所以希望用十戎歌嘅形式可以靈活同人性化啲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZjbjkwHXQKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZjbjkwHXQKE&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=6dd2f8e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZjbjkwHXQKE</a><br />\n形式/旋律方面會參考翻艾粒嘅十戎歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為洗腦易記，啲詞唔洗岩音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 咁好啦，brainstorm 時間開始，大家一齊討論有邊十樣野要戎/小心謹慎/一定要做啦！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好 掛住狂捉鬼<br />\n2. 唔好 鬆懈嘉年華<br />\n3. TBC<br />\n<br />\n以上頭兩個唔岩心水嘅，各位都可以換左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，或者唔夠嘅十二戎都可以，但建議只提重點，以方便記歌詞！！！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊諗齊十戎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，報仇！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0da703a91425d77844d1f7b306d140f724436480","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"1/10推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a750fd69cf8be695485babaa457c31d3009811","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:13.000Z","msg":"2/10推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e956be271aa537f76967610bf2e46a3aebd6f433","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:26.000Z","msg":"3/10推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420e94c77fc7a6faf2ad55e6adfc5ad77d0c6981","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:37.000Z","msg":"4/10推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b8b084a7070c5e3e6a17ca8676d754758fac32","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"5/10 pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ddef13119a196d52845038e0b7e243440347a6","tid":1725383,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"6/10 pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a76289732